<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>  
    <title>Services</title>
</head>
<body>
      <style>
            /* General Styles */
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                background-color: #f5f5f5;
                color: #333;
            }
            header {
                background-color: #4285f4;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            nav {
                background-color: #333;
                padding: 30px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            nav a {
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
                margin: 0 10px;
            }
            main {
                padding: 100px;
            }
            footer {
                background-color: #333;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                position: fixed;
                bottom: 0;
                width: 100%;
            }
            /* Unique Styles for Services */
            .services-container {
                background-color: #fff;
                padding: 40px;
                border-radius: 20px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                max-width: 800px;
                margin: 20px auto;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .services-container h2 {
                color: #4285f4;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .service-item {
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                padding: 20px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            }
            .service-item:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }
            .service-item h3 {
                color: #4285f4;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .service-item p {
                color: #666;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Services</h1>
        </header>
        <nav>
            <a href="/user/Home">Home</a>
            <a href="/user/RecycleProducts">Recycling Products</a>
            <a href="/user/SellTrash">Sell Waste</a>
            <a href="/user/BuyTrash">Buy Waste</a>
            <a href="/user/AboutWM">About Waste Management</a>
            <a href="/user/Service">Services</a>
            <a href="/user/Aboutus">About Us</a>
            <a href="/user/Typeswaste">Types of Waste</a>
        </nav>
        <main>
            <div class="services-container">
                <h2>Our Services</h2>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Waste Collection</h3>
                    <p>We provide efficient waste collection services to ensure proper disposal and recycling.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Recycling Solutions</h3>
                    <p>Our innovative recycling solutions help reduce environmental impact and promote sustainability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Education and Awareness</h3>
                    <p>We offer educational programs and awareness campaigns to promote responsible waste management practices.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Rewards System</h3>
                    <p>Through our rewards system, users earn points for waste disposal, which can be redeemed for various products or bill payments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Waste Image Recognition</h3>
                    <p>We utilize AI and ML algorithms to recognize the image quality and quantity of waste uploaded by users.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Product Marketplace</h3>
                    <p>Our platform features a marketplace where users can buy recycled products and natural manure using their accumulated points.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Bill Payment System</h3>
                    <p>Users can use their rewards points for paying bills such as electricity, gas, etc., through our secure bill payment system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p style="color: rgb(229, 255, 0)">&copy; 2024 Waste Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
